"{\"uid\": \"flotrack.org-articles-12757207-aau-junior-olympics-track-and-field-2024-results-on-day-6\", \"text\": \"Redlands Invitational  Adidas Indoor Nationals  Texas Distance Festival  Chandler Rotary Invite  W&L Outdoor T&F Carnival  Run Rome the Marathon  David Noble Relays  Emory Thrills in the Hills  WashU Distance Carnival  Jim Taylor Duals  Doc Jopson Invitational  2026 FSU Relays  Continental Tour: Maurie Plant Meet  WashU Invite  Monmouth Home Opener  5 national records fell during track events on Day 6 of the AAU Junior Olympics, including a 27 year long record in the 110m hurdles.  Zacchaeus Brocks went 13.73 in the 15-16 boys 110m hurdles final, winning gold and setting a new national record.  Day 6 featured finals in the 1500m for ages 8 and under to 12, as well as finals in the 80mh, 100mh and 110mh.  The 2024 Junior Olympics Track and Field competition isstreaming live on FloTrack, MileSplit and the FloSports app.Highlights, replays and breaking news are on both platforms.  Do not miss all the track and field season action streaming on FloTrack.Check out the FloTrack schedule for more events.  Video footage from each event will be archived and stored in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.  Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.  \\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\"}"